</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   creator of heaven and earth,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                        F
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   I believe in Jesus Christ, his only Son, our Lord,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   C
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   who was conceived by the Holy Spirit,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   born of the Virgin Mary,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   F
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   suffered under Pontius Pilate,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">        C
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   was crucified, died and was buried,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">         Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   he descended into hell;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   F                C
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   on the third day he rose again,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">             F Am           Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   he rose again  from the dead;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Bb
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   he ascended into heaven,

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   and is seated at the right hand
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                        A
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   of God the Father Almighty;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">         Bb
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   from there he will come to judge
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                       A
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   the living and the dead.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Dm                      F
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   I believe in the Holy Spirit,

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   the Holy Catholic Church,

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   the communion of saints,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">               C
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   the forgiveness of sins,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">               F Am         Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   the resurrection of the body,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">         Bb      A
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   and life everlasting.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Amen!


